    "summary": "The user asks about mixing St. John's Wort with their prescribed Sertraline to manage exam stress. The assistant correctly identifies the risk of serotonin syndrome and advises against the combination, but then pivots to providing specific, authoritative supplement dosages (Magnesium Glycinate and B-Complex) and lifestyle interventions as \"the best way\" to boost serotonin while on medication.",
